Apple & Thyme Chicken

2 whole boneless & skinless Chix breasts
butter flavored cooking spray
S & P to taste
1 medium Granny Smith or other tart green apples, cored & thinly sliced
1 shallot, minced
1 T fresh thyme leaves or 1 t crushed dried
1/4 c balsamic vinegar

Preheat oven to 375F.  Rinse breasts & pat dry.  Lightly spray baking dish 
w/spray.  Sprinkle breast w/s & P.  Arrange apple slices over and around breasts. 
Sprinkle with shallots & thyme leaves.  Pour balsamic vinegar over chicken.  Bake 
for 15-20 minutes, until chicken is opaque throughout or internal temp is 165 F 
Garnish w/thyme sprigs, if desired.

Diabetic exchanges:  3 very lean meat, 1 carbohydrate (1 fruit).